Wstbot is a bot for the IRC network with extensible features.
It is developed by wst, wstcode@gmail.com.

========================
Dependencies
========================

* python 3.1+
* cherrypy for features using the webserver
* pyyaml

========================
Installation
========================

* Edit wstbot.conf.EXAMPLE and rename it to wstbot.conf.
* Rename data/regex.yaml.EXAMPLE to data/regex.yaml (and add some sites if you want to).

To run the bot and the server, enter the wstbot directory and execute:

python3 -m botserver.server
python3 -m wstbot

